pe=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration=
: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; =
border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> alleged glass house</=
a>:</p>
<blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">=C2=A0The Wall Street Journal reported last mo=
nth that the Justice Department is investigating Tesla=E2=80=99s use of com=
pany resources on a secret project that was described internally as a house=
 for Musk.=C2=A0</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The house effort was known within the carmaker=
 as =E2=80=9CProject 42,=E2=80=9D and plans called for an expansive glass b=
uilding to be constructed near Tesla=E2=80=99s Austin-area factory and head=
quarters.=C2=A0</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The Securities and Exchange Commission has ope=
ned a separate civil investigation into the project, the Journal has report=
ed.=C2=A0</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">On X, the social-media platform formerly known=
 as Twitter, Musk has said there isn=E2=80=99t a glass house =E2=80=9Cbuilt=
, under construction or planned.=E2=80=9D He didn=E2=80=99t address past wo=
rk or plans; neither he nor his representatives have responded to requests =
for comment.=C2=A0</p>
</blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">I have <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergb=
usiness.com/click/32776778.258423/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGlua=
