lPW5ld3NsZXR0ZXImdXRtX3Rlcm09MjMwOTIwJnV0bV9jYW1wYWlnbj1tb25leXN0dWZm/607f0=
7ceef4b8524a319a23cB69ce2f82" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope=
" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !importa=
nt; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-s=
tyle: solid; background-color: #ccc;">  written about the house before</a>:=
</p>
<blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Look honestly I think spending mil=
lions of dollars to build a giant glass house for Elon Musk right near Tesl=
a headquarters is a=C2=A0<em>good</em>=C2=A0use of corporate funds? Keep an=
 eye on him. Really if the board had thought of this I would be praising it=
 as an innovative corporate governance idea. You can=E2=80=99t necessarily =
make Elon Musk warn you when he=E2=80=99s going to=C2=A0tweet something mat=
erial=C2=A0or go buy another company to run full-time, but you=C2=A0<em>can=
=C2=A0</em>give him the gift of a glass house and get yourself a telescope.=
</p></blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">But also just Elon Musk has a lot of weird whi=
ms and if you are an investor or director at one of his companies it makes =
some sense to spend shareholder money to=C2=A0satisfy his whims so that he =
will be content and=C2=A0devote more of his attention to your company, sinc=
e his attention does, empirically, seem to make most of his companies more =
valuable. (Not Twitter?<a class=3D"footnote-index" href=3D"#footnote-6" sty=
le=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width=
: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: none !important; =
background-color: transparent !important; display: inline-block;">
<span>[6]</span>
</a>) And so in some informal sense Elon Musk=E2=80=99s compensation-and-pe=
rks package at his companies is =E2=80=9Cwhatever he wants, just keep him h=
appy.=E2=80=9D At SpaceX that is a basically plausible package. At Tesla it=
=E2=80=99s=C2=A0<em>possibly a crime.</em></p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">I <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusine=
ss.com/click/32776778.258423/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2=
FydGljbGVzLzIwMjMtMDktMDYvc3BhY2V4LWxvYW5lZC1lbG9uLW11c2stc29tZS1tb25leT9jb=
