<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">A basic fact about the mergers-and-acquisition=
s advisory business is that, if you run a company, and an investment banker=
 comes in to pitch you on doing an acquisition:</p>
<ol style=3D"list-style-type: decimal; padding-left: 40px; margin: 16px 0;"=
>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">That acquisition might or might not b=
e a good idea for your company. In general the <a href=3D"https://link.mail=
.bloombergbusiness.com/click/32776778.258423/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cud3NqLmNvbS9idX=
NpbmVzcy9kZWFscy9tLWEtY2FuLXBheS1vZmYtYnV0LWl0cy1mYXItZnJvbS1hLXN1cmUtdGhpb=
mctMmMwZGQzOGI/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB23629b29" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" it=
emscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decor=
ation: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000=
000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> track record of =
companies doing acquisitions</a> is mixed to bad.=C2=A0</li>=09<li style=3D=
"margin-bottom: 5px;">It=E2=80=99s definitely a good idea for the banker! I=
f you hire her bank to do the acquisition, it will get a big fee and she=E2=
=80=99ll get a big bonus.<a class=3D"footnote-index" href=3D"#footnote-7" s=
tyle=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-wid=
th: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: none !important=
; background-color: transparent !important; display: inline-block;">
<span>[7]</span>
</a>=C2=A0If the deal turns out to be a dud for you, that=E2=80=99s not her=
 problem.<a class=3D"footnote-index" href=3D"#footnote-8" style=3D"color: #=
000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-=
bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: none !important; background-col=
or: transparent !important; display: inline-block;">
<span>[8]</span>
</a>
</li>
</ol>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Everybody who has ever been pitched on doing a=
 merger probably knows this. The banker sitting across from you is your tru=
sted adviser, sure, but she=E2=80=99s also selling you something, and it=E2=
=80=99s your job to figure out if it=E2=80=99s a good idea for you. You kno=
w it=E2=80=99s a good idea for her.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">We have <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloomberg=
business.com/click/32776778.258423/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGlu=
aW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjMtMDgtMjEvZXZlcnlvbmUtd2FudHMtYS1waWVjZS1vZi1zY3VscHR=
vcj9jbXBpZD1CQkQwOTIwMjNfTU9ORVlTVFVGRiZ1dG1fbWVkaXVtPWVtYWlsJnV0bV9zb3VyY2=
U9bmV3c2xldHRlciZ1dG1fdGVybT0yMzA5MjAmdXRtX2NhbXBhaWduPW1vbmV5c3R1ZmY/607f0=
7ceef4b8524a319a23cB92666f60" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope=
" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !importa=
nt; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-s=
tyle: solid; background-color: #ccc;">  talked</a> a lot in recent months a=
bout Goldman Sachs Group Inc. partners who are disgruntled with the regime =
of Chief Executive Officer David Solomon, who runs Goldman like a normal pu=
blic company rather than like the private partnership that it was for many =
years, and that it sort of pretended to be for another 20 years after that.=
 (Usual disclosure: I used to work at Goldman.)</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Here is =E2=80=9C<a href=3D"https://link.mail.=
bloombergbusiness.com/click/32776778.258423/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYnVzaW5lc3NpbnN=
pZGVyLmNvbS9nb2xkbWFuLXNhY2hzLWRhdmlkLXNvbG9tb24tY2VvLXBhcnRuZXJzLWRlcGFydH=
