Wx0aHJ1JnV0bV9jYW1wYWlnbj1JbnNpZGVyX1RvZGF5/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB81fd12=
f5" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=
=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: =
1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-c=
olor: #ccc;">Why former Goldman Sachs partners say they left the firm</a>=
=E2=80=9D by Dakin Campbell at Insider, based on interviews with six anonym=
ous former partners. The basic complaints about Solomon boil down to (1) he=
 treats the partners like employees rather than like partners and (2) Goldm=
an put a lot of chips into a bet on consumer banking that didn=E2=80=99t wo=
rk out, and it is now doing an <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusine=
ss.com/click/32776778.258423/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cud3NqLmNvbS9maW5hbmNlL2Jhbmtpbm=
cvZ29sZG1hbi1zYWNocy1pbi1hZHZhbmNlZC10YWxrcy10by1zZWxsLWdyZWVuc2t5LWluLWJpZ=
y1zdGVwLWluLWNvbnN1bWVyLXJldHJlYXQtYzAyMjFmNjc_bW9kPWhwX2xlYWRfcG9zNg/607f0=
7ceef4b8524a319a23cBab82242b" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope=
" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !importa=
nt; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-s=
tyle: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> embarrassing and costly retreat</a>.=
</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">These complaints are related=C2=A0in the sense=
 that they are both partly about nostalgia for the good old days, when Gold=
man was an elite player in high finance that would never deign to do small-=
dollar consumer business, and when the partners were the elite=C2=A0within =
the elite who were running the show. Now =E2=80=9Cpartner=E2=80=9D is a cou=
rtesy title and Goldman is giving out toasters when you open a checking acc=
ount, feh.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">I often <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloomberg=
business.com/click/32776778.258423/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGlu=
aW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMTktMDMtMDYvYmUtY2FyZWZ1bC13ZWFyaW5nLWplYW5zLWF0LWdvbGR=
tYW4_Y21waWQ9QkJEMDkyMDIzX01PTkVZU1RVRkYmdXRtX21lZGl1bT1lbWFpbCZ1dG1fc291cm=
NlPW5ld3NsZXR0ZXImdXRtX3Rlcm09MjMwOTIwJnV0bV9jYW1wYWlnbj1tb25leXN0dWZm/607f=
07ceef4b8524a319a23cB81100f2d" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscop=
e" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !import=
ant; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-=
style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">  quote</a> John Whitehead=E2=80=99s=
 <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/32776778.258423/a=
HR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYnVzaW5lc3NpbnNpZGVyLmNvbS9qb2huLXdoaXRlaGVhZC10ZW4tY29tbWFu=
ZG1lbnRzLTIwMTUtMg/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cBc579fc33" itemprop=3D"StoryLink=
" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-d=
ecoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: =
#000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> Investment B=
anking Services commandments</a> around here. =E2=80=9CDon=E2=80=99t waste =
your time going after business we don=E2=80=99t really want,=E2=80=9D is on=
e of them. =E2=80=9CIt=E2=80=99s just as easy to get a first-rate piece of =
business as a second-rate one,=E2=80=9D is another. My favorite is: =E2=80=
=9CImportant people like to deal with other important people. Are you one?=
=E2=80=9D You can see why some Goldman partners who grew up with those comm=
andments might be grumbling now. They see Goldman going after business they=
 don=E2=80=99t really want, and they don=E2=80=99t feel as important as the=
y used to.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Also though <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloom=
bergbusiness.com/click/32776778.258423/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYnVzaW5lc3NpbnNpZGVy=
LmNvbS9nb2xkbWFuLXNhY2hzLWRhdmlkLXNvbG9tb24tY2VvLXBhcnRuZXJzLWRlcGFydHVyZXM=
tc3RyYXRlZ3ktMjAyMy05P3V0bV9tZWRpdW09bmV3c2xldHRlciZ1dG1fc291cmNlPVNhaWx0aH=
J1JnV0bV9jYW1wYWlnbj1JbnNpZGVyX1RvZGF5/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cC81fd12f5" i=
temprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"co=
lor: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; b=
order-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: =
#ccc;">there=E2=80=99s this anecdote</a>:</p>
<blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The bank is also now selling its GreenSky poin=
t-of-sale financing business. Yet the acquisition, which Goldman made in 20=
21 for $2.2 billion, still rankles Goldmanites. The deal never made sense t=
o many people inside Goldman, especially those in its investment-banking di=
vision who had spent their careers advising corporate executives on takeove=
r targets. =E2=80=A6</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">It's not just internal people who have noticed=
. One former partner who spoke with Insider said that in calling on clients=
, people had had to answer for Goldman's consumer-banking missteps.=C2=A0</=
p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">"It's kind of embarrassing when you are showin=
g up to a client pitching for M&amp;A business, position yourself as the be=
st M&amp;A advisor, pointing to these credentials, and our own deals have b=
een an absolute mess," the person said. "The number of jokes clients make, =
and there is some truth, why hire you to do M&amp;A if you can't even do yo=
ur own M&amp;A." =C2=A0</p>
</blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Oh come on! I do not believe for a second that=
 some Goldman investment banker showed up to pitch a merger and the client =
was like =E2=80=9Cnope, not taking your merger pitch because Goldman bought=
 GreenSky, proving that you=E2=80=99re dummies like everyone else.=E2=80=9D=
 I mean, sure, as a joke. But the idea here is that previously Goldman woul=
d pitch M&amp;A deals and the clients were like =E2=80=9Coh wow Goldman say=
s I should buy this company, that must be right, they are very smart and th=
eir M&amp;A pitch is=C2=A0a disinterested search for truth,=E2=80=9D but no=
w that GreenSky didn=E2=80=99t work the clients realize that Goldman is fal=
lible. Everyone always knew the M&amp;A pitches were fallible! Still, fine,=
 I concede that it is a little funny to make fun of your M&amp;A banker for=
 her bank=E2=80=99s bad M&amp;A deals.</p>
<table class=3D"header" width=3D"100%" border=3D"0" cellspacing=3D"0" cellp=
